title: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609 [Regression] Color orange doesn't work. Description: When setting the color to orange, the color does not display as expected. Steps to reproduce: 1. Insert a report item. 2. Set the color or background color to orange.
OB: The report item color does not display as orange.
EB: Preview. Expected result: The report item should display with the color orange.
SR: 3. Run the preview and observe the report item color.
